{"article_id":"lN1Zxh6qQoqwEd8f","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US Attorney General William Barr faced off for the first time Tuesday with House lawmakers about his handling of the Mueller report .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"Now he 's back on the hot seat","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"testifying before a Senate subcommittee Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Barr is responding to Democratic criticism over his summary of Mueller .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"He says","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"the redacted report will be released next week ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"but that may not be good enough for Democrats .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"`` I do think","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"it 's important","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"that the public have an opportunity","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"to learn the results of the special counsel 's work , ''","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"Barr said .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Testifying before the House Appropriations Committee Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Barr stuck to his promise","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"to deliver a redacted version of the report in coming days .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"`` And so I think","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that from my standpoint , within a week I will be in a position","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to release the report to the public ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and then I will engage with the chairmen of both Judiciary Committees about that report , and about any further requests","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that they have , ''","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Barr said .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Although Barr was officially on Capitol Hill","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"to testify about the Justice Department 's budget ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"many lawmakers circled back to the Russia investigation .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"Rep. Nita Lowey","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"said ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"`` I must say","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"it is extraordinary to evaluate hundreds of pages of evidence legal documents , and finding","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"based on a 22-month-long inquiry ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and make definitive legal conclusions in less than 48 hours .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Even for someone","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who has done this job before ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"I would argue","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"it 's more suspicious than impressive . ''","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Democrats have been critical of Barr 's approach","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"and want to see the complete conclusions of the Mueller investigation ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"threatening to issue a subpoena","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"if they do n't get what they want .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Barr addressed scrutiny of his four-page letter","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"summarizing his main conclusions from Mueller 's nearly 400-page report ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"stating the Mueller team 's finding","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that neither President Trump or his campaign conspired or coordinated with Russia 's interference with the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Lowey said ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"`` All we have is your four-page report","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"which seems to cherry pick","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"to draw most favorable for president . ''","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"He defended his decision","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"to release that letter instead of summaries","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"written by the special counsel .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"any summary","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"regardless of who prepares it","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"not only runs the risk of ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"you know ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"being under-inclusive or over-inclusive","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"but also would trigger a lot of discussion and analysis","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that really should await everything coming out at once , ''","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Barr said .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` I tried to use as much of the special counsel 's own language","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"as I could .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"They were just stating the bottom line conclusions . ''","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"House Republicans are ready to move on .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Rep. Tom Graves","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"( R-GA )","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"said ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"`` No collusion , no obstruction .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"It 's over ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"it 's done . ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"`` Well , the letter - the letter speaks for itself , ''","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Barr said .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Meanwhile , Barr is also investigating","depth":3},{"id":72,"text":"whether the FBI abused its authority","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"in getting wiretaps on Trump aides","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"that fueled the investigation","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"leading to the Mueller probe .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"The attorney general testifies before the Senate Wednesday ,","depth":3},{"id":77,"text":"and he says","depth":4},{"id":78,"text":"he will answer more questions from Congress next month","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"after the full Mueller report has been released .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":150,"right":158,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":100,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":91,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":82,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":0,"right":81,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":81,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":3,"right":89,"relation":"context","nuclearit